## Contributing

To contribute to these guidelines:

1. Follow the [Core Principles](mdc:core/core-principles.mdc)
2. Maintain consistency as outlined in the [Core Principles](mdc:core/core-principles.mdc#consistency-requirements)
3. Adhere to [Code Style](mdc:core/code-style.mdc) guidelines
4. Maintain [Consistency Patterns](mdc:core/consistency-patterns.mdc)
5. Update cross-references appropriately
6. Keep the INDEX.md current
